Name: brainstem intraparenchymal clear cell meningioma
Definition: A brain stem cancer in the infratentorial region of the brain in childhood
Synonym: Intraparenchymal Clear cell meningioma of the Brainstem

Name: chordoid meningioma
Definition: A cervical adenosquamous carcinoma that is a rare form and is composed of cells with a glass-like cytoplasm.
